::Slayer::

Slayer stops above some spark energy readings. He frowns. Prebon was 
among the bots there. Slayer flies slightly lower, armind his missile 
launchers. Aiming at the ground in the spot that the energy readings 
were under, he fires two missiles, blowing some earth apart there. He 
growls. There had to be an easier way to do this.
